_sText:
This map was created by CampinClams. He made this map about a year ago. I'm just submitting it. He is Fully aware I am doing so. This is CampinClams first map.

There are T's and CT's in this map. You start off on glass. When the round begins you can buy your weapons. I would preferably buy a shotgun. Shoot the glass to drop down to the trampoline.

CC stands for CampinClams. Not Chery Clan.

Enjoy CampinClams map. :)
